Floyd's death has been described as directly evoking the player's emotions because the story and gameplay are aligned.<ref>"By aligning the story with the gameplay, you evoke the emotions in the player directly, without having to appeal to a sometimes vain hope of sympathy. ... Examples range from the classic "Death of Floyd" in ''Planetfall'', where a selfless robot helps your character--you-- directly..." {{Cite journal
